schools.name: Boerne - Samuel V Champion High School

data.description: Step into a realm of opulence as you enter the open entryway of this four bedroom, three full and two half bath home in Front Gate, where an ornate wrought iron railing staircase beckons you into its luxuriously spacious surroundings.  The designer touch resonates throughout, with wood-look tile flooring laying the foundation for a stunning family room featuring elevated ceilings reaching towards the second story, all illuminated by upgraded chandelier-style lighting and the warm glow of an inviting fireplace.  The home's island kitchen is a veritable chef's paradise, fitted with a robust six-burner gas cooktop, shining stainless steel appliances, dual ovens, and stunning modern white cabinetry, all anchored by a dishwasher for quick, easy cleanup after get-togethers with loved ones.  Retreat to the grandeur of the primary bedroom, offering a private sanctuary and an ultra-modern en suite bath equipped with separate vanities, a standalone bathtub, a tile shower that makes innovative use of a glass window into the room to allow for light to brighten up your morning routine, and a custom walk-in closet designed to impress.  Beyond necessity, find pleasure in the formal dining room poised for memorable gatherings and a study secluded by elegant glass French doors.  You'll also find an additional secondary bedroom downstairs.  The upstairs game room with breathtaking views offers endless entertainment options.  The true essence of this home as an entertainer's paradise shines through as you step out to the covered patio, where ceiling fans and Bluetooth speakers await, enhancing the entertainment value of your heated saltwater pool complete with waterfall, spa, and generous deck space.  There's no shortage of exceptional features in this architectural treasure - a versatile media or flex room, a spacious three-car tandem garage, and thoughtful touches like a high backyard fence ensuring privacy, convenient under-stairs storage, a modern tankless water heater, and a water softener all serve to heighten the living experience.  This house is not simply a home; it's a haven of luxury and calm, eager to become the backdrop to you living your best life.  Embrace the opportunity to claim this magnificent residence as your own and bask in the lifestyle you've longed to lead.
